{
    "name": "Stencil Mask",
    "description": [
        "This example shows using the stencil buffer for masking. It draws 6 planes, forming a cube, each plane with a different stencil value. It then draws 7 scenes of moving objects, each set to only draw when the stencilReference value matches the value in the stencil buffer."
